SR25 contains nutrient data for over 8,100 food items and up to 146 food components, such as vitamins, minerals, amino acids, and fatty acids. It replaces the previous release, SR24 issued in September 2011.</dct:description>         <dcat:keyword>amino-acids</dcat:keyword>         <dcat:keyword>composition-of-food</dcat:keyword>
